Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的所在？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我可就愛莫能助了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者也有不知道的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我知道它在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們又打算對Veda如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪回它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda原本就是為輔佐我們而設計製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算使用Veda做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊歐利亞構築這項計劃的真意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為即將到來的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即將到來的對話？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來也並非那麼萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淪為階下囚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷特納爾她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她射傷拉塞先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還把米蕾娜抓作人質
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷特納爾她自稱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果有什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人質性命難保
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和艾紐作為同類型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思想能夠相連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 按計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦內的系統被…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷…雷特納爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還來得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想再住前走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我在這
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只你能用腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦內系統被病毒感染？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩組搜尋米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐請去艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 艾紐去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯小姐你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 忘記了你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C級別的腦量子使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有缺陷的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是一切的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為上校報仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清英 史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算拋棄我一個人走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願意和我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看到世界的變革喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外附贈Cherudim
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何必真的打中 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人質被救走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非要製作成女的 最後因為感情壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐用小艇逃生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這系統是怎麼回事 太不順手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三閘門自動打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後部閘門也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動Cherudim和00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 一時疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去向利馮茲解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 必須優先奪回0-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用TRANS-AM了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕傷到這台機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有優秀的戰術預報員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser合體模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統控制權被00…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如洛克昂所說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠談不上萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已 只能對0-Raiser死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 帶件禮物回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不算過份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser的功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐．雷特納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊啊 瞄準狙擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為何身在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何加入Katharon…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入天人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不爭氣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾．狄蘭提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的覺悟就只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾．狄蘭提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說身體欠佳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你需要新的藥方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馬克 我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提供藥物抑制你體內細胞異常造成的侵害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你主動要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為實現沒有紛爭的統一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為父母報仇 向Gundam討還血債
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你寄予厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台Regnant也是專程為你帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你成為人類中首位變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引導這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 路易斯．阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德 艦內系統狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航行戰鬥系統受到相當大破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經清除病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但被破壞的數據多達3456
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還被變革者帶走了部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新構築需要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最短2210
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 雷特納爾她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在專心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人馬上會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 0-Raiser的修理進度如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更換了整個駕駛艙部件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是Raiser系統需要時間調整
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時別指望00
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會出現在戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為他們會放過這次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你提醒我也會做自己該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手是變革者 是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扳機一扣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逞強\N扳機一扣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻我來扣動扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時恨我便是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝腔作勢了 毛孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有與她戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不戰的理由更強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞 Seravee準備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的駕駛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道無法令人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就靠你的Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E探測器反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從速度判斷 是敵人部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦船系統報銷 00半殘廢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘的Gundam好對付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西林 我們的目的是俘虜00
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她也出一份力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新製造的Regnant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是初陣 但期待你的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3台…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人雖然數量不多 但是有MA協同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同於之前的機型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彎曲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這威力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別激動 萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好男人都讓你毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇性重逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深愛的女子是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂 致命的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐引走了一台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我們搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級轟擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高濃度壓縮粒子 釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級轟擊被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arios損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim遠離作戰宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差少許
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 Shield Bit 強襲模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們真心相愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在虛偽的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是謊言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新讓你成為我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說你不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊…萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西就要奪過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歸我了 00
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到這裡來 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…愚蠢的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者是引導人類的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 作為高等種群的絕對支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法容忍被人類視為平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見識實力上的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…我其實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慶幸自己是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則無法與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許永遠只能在這世界的某處與你擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你活著也沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 我們確實真心相愛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你把艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她曾想回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類 而非變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明真心相愛 卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我和路易絲也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聲音在迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功改變人生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去親人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨的鎖鏈只會奪走人的生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 革新之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.57,0:24:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那邁出那一步
